	<text id="Rabbit_Unit_Encounter_Creature_TETH_2">連熱身都算不上</text>

	<text id="Rabbit_Unit_Encounter_Creature_HE_0">危險度：中。</text>
	<text id="Rabbit_Unit_Encounter_Creature_HE_1">就像是後巷內那些東西的等級。</text>
	<text id="Rabbit_Unit_Encounter_Creature_HE_2">真是奇特的怪物。</text>
	<text id="Rabbit_Unit_Encounter_Creature_HE_3">這種怪物廢墟裡要多少有多少。</text>
	<text id="Rabbit_Unit_Encounter_Creature_HE_4">正好活動下筋骨。</text>

	<text id="Rabbit_Unit_Encounter_Creature_WAW_0">危險度：高。</text>
	<text id="Rabbit_Unit_Encounter_Creature_WAW_1">好久沒對付這麼危險的目標了。</text>
	<text id="Rabbit_Unit_Encounter_Creature_WAW_2">是把郊區的東西關在這裡了嗎？</text>
	<text id="Rabbit_Unit_Encounter_Creature_WAW_3">為什麼不把這些傢伙用在翼的戰爭上？</text>
	<text id="Rabbit_Unit_Encounter_Creature_WAW_4">這地方也是個瘋人院。</text>
	
	<text id="Rabbit_Unit_Encounter_Creature_ALEPH_0">危險度：極高。</text>
